OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew chief fire officer     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffacing harassment claims   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The man brought in to lead a Welsh fire
OL,6, service rocked by claims of poor       
OL,7, behaviour is himself facing allegations
OL,8, of harassment and discrimination.      
OL,10,FThe Welsh government sent commissioners
OL,11,Finto South Wales Fire and Rescue       
OL,12,FService after a damning report about   
OL,13,Fharassment and misogyny.               
OL,15,FThey appointed Stuart Millington, who  
OL,16,Fis facing an employment tribunal, to be
OL,17,Fan interim chief fire officer.         
OL,19,FIt is understood Mr Millington has     
OL,20,Fdenied the allegations.                
